description: Two fishermen on a boat pull in a fishing net brimming not with fish, but a large, tangled mass of anthropomorphic frogs wearing various brightly colored outfits. The scene presents an absurd, surreal situation where a common fishing activity yields an entirely unexpected and bizarre 'catch.' The lead fisherman comments on the sheer quantity of the bizarre haul, underscoring the unexpected nature of the event.
caption: “I’m not sure, Al, but we sure got into a mess of ‘em.”
